<h2>Fonts</h2>

<p>Our main font is Museo Sans Rounded and is used in weights 300 (default) and 500 (bold, headings, links, buttons).</p>

<p>Museo is not a system font, so it must be purchased and licensed for web use. It is available to license from the following vendors, as well as many others:</p>

<ul>
	<li><a href="https://typekit.com/fonts/museo-sans-rounded">Museo Sans Rounded on Typekit</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://www.myfonts.com/fonts/exljbris/museo-sans-rounded/">Museo Sans Rounded on MyFonts</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://www.fonts.com/font/exljbris/museo-sans/rounded-300/web-font">Museo Sans Rounded on fonts.com</a></li>
</ul>

<p>For Cryllic alphabets, we use <a href="https://www.myfonts.com/fonts/exljbris/museo-sans-cyrillic/webfont_preview.html">Museo Sans Cyrillic</a>.</p>

