<h2>Colour Adjustment Utilities</h2>

<p>The following utility classes will allow you to change the colour of your text. Be careful to display text on a contrasting background to aid readability.</p>

<div class="sg-example">
	<h3 class="sg-example__heading">Example</h3>

	<div class="sg-example__preview">
		<% colors[:palette].each do |name, value| %>
		<p class="u-color--<%= name %>">Lorem Ipsum dolor sit amet</p>
		<% end %>
	</div>

	<code class="sg-example__code">
		<% colors[:palette].each do |name, value| %>&lt;p class="u-color--<%= name %>"&lt;Lorem Ipsum dolor sit amet&lt;/p&gt;<br><% end %>
	</code>
</div>

